longBusinessSummary: Matsui Securities Co., Ltd. provides online securities brokerage services to retail investors in Japan. It offers brokerage services of stocks, futures, and options; services for underwriting, offering, and secondary distribution and solicitation for selling; and foreign exchange margin trading services, as well as investment trusts and asset management business. The company was founded in 1918 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
